                    "options": []
                },
                {
                    "id": "6d8dbbbfe2be4045b2bba",
                    "stepText": "Using the photon energy relation $!$E = \\frac{hc}{\\lambda}$!$, calculate the energy of a photon for $!$\\lambda_1$!$. Compute $!$\\frac{hc}{\\lambda_1}$!$ in Joules.",
