                    "options": []
                },
                {
                    "id": "6f388b75e6a6491898f4c",
                    "stepText": "Now, using the photoelectric equation $!$E_k = hf - \\phi$!$, determine the work function for the first wavelength by subtracting the kinetic energy from the photon energy. Compute $!$\\phi_1 = \\frac{hc}{\\lambda_1} - eV_1$!$ in Joules.",
